Package: FPKM
Title: Calculate FPKM from RNA-seq Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Veronica Gosnell", email = "veronicagosnell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is designed to analyze RNA-seq data. It provides functions for 
    FPKM calculation, transformation, normalization, and visualization with
    boxplots, heatmaps, and Principle Component Analysis (PCA). It also contains
    functions for exploration of gene expression data, including tools for filtering 
    low expression genes and summarizing expression profiles.
License: CC0
